                <h2>Maintaining Optimal Health</h2>
                <p>Implement these best practices to keep your cat healthy:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Exercise:</strong> Encourage playtime to keep your cat active and prevent obesity.</li>
                    <li><strong>Grooming:</strong> Regular brushing helps to reduce shedding and hairballs, and keep their coat in good condition.</li>
                    <li><strong>Routine Checks:</strong> Schedule regular vet check-ups for vaccinations, dental care, and general health assessments.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Maintain a consistent care routine and monitor any changes in behavior or health.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

